markets.title: Chinese LLM better than OpenAI, Google, or Anthropic before 2025?
markets.subtitle: Before Jan 1, 2025
markets.rules_primary: If a Chinese LLM is ranked higher than the top LLM by either OpenAI, Google, or Anthropic, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The overall ranking will be used to settle the Contract, not the Elo score. A Chinese LLM only has to be higher than the top ranked LLM by any of the 3 companies for the market to resolve to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: If this event occurs, the market will close the following 10:00 AM ET.
